# Eden Novel — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WEB (Replit / Vite dev-server)
#   Set these in Replit's Secrets panel (the lock icon).
#   You can use either the bare name (GROK_API_KEY) OR the VITE_-prefixed name
#   (VITE_GROK_API_KEY). The Vite configs automatically bridge both forms.
#
# APK (Android build)
#   Copy this file to .env before running `npm run build:android`.
#   Keys baked into the APK bundle act as the DEFAULT fallback — users can
#   override any key at runtime via the in-app API Key Setup screen.
#   If a user enters their own key it takes priority over the .env value.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Amazon Bedrock  (ABSK… key — region us-east-1)
BEDROCK_API_KEY=
# VITE_BEDROCK_API_KEY=   # alternative VITE_-prefixed form (both work)

# Google Gemini
GEMINI_API_KEY=
# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=

# xAI Grok
GROK_API_KEY=
# VITE_GROK_API_KEY=

# OpenAI
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=

# HuggingFace
HF_TOKEN=
# VITE_HF_TOKEN=

# Anthropic Claude
CLAUDE_API_KEY=
# VITE_CLAUDE_API_KEY=

# DeepSeek
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# VITE_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=

# ─── Server-side only (api-server, never exposed to browser) ─────────────────
# MongoDB (used by api-server)
# MONGODB_URI=

# Firebase Admin SDK (server-side auth — set in Replit Secrets)
# FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=eden-novel
# FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=
# FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY=
